author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Panasonic Whisper Remodel LED bathroom fan installation…I chose this fan because it will add more light and ventilate the bathroom. The first step is to add the adjustable bracket. Then I wire the fan and add insulated ductwork. All this can be done without attic access. This a great affordable option, here’s a link https://bit.ly/47ZwNxk to check it out. Many thanks to Panasonic for providing to fan to my client 🔥#bathroomventilation #bathroomremodel #panasoniciaq #homerenovation #sponsored
